metadata.name: Foreshadowing
metadata.description: For days we made the city our playground, Climbing, tunneling and train surfing in the pursuit of seeing all Paris had to offer. Late in the day we split the group in half, two of us going to surf and two set taking the photo we'd set up. after an exhilarating ride and a sprint to safety we had our final result, a dream photo in front of the Eiffel Tower with a special touch to make it all the more unique.
